code: @Override protected ServletEndpoint createServletEndpoint(String endpointUri, ServletComponent component, URI httpUri) throws Exception {     return new WebsocketEndpoint(endpointUri, (WebsocketComponent) component, httpUri). }

WebSocketStore getWebSocketStore(String name) {     WebSocketStore store.     synchronized (stores) {         store = stores.get(name).         if (store == null) {             store = new MemoryWebSocketStore().             stores.put(name, store).         }     }     return store. }
